quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,32,"For that reason, We prescribed for the children of Israel that whoever kills anyone without (it being a killing of the murderer of) someone, or due to corruption in the earth, then it will be as if he killed all human beings; and whoever saves a life then it will be as if he saved the lives of all human beings. And Our messengers had come to them with clear proofs, then even after that many of them are committers of excesses in the earth"
  5,33,"Indeed, the penalty for those who wage war against God and His Messenger and spread terrorism in the land is death, crucifixion, cutting off their hands and feet on opposite sides, or exile from the land. This ˹penalty˺ is a disgrace for them in this world, and they will suffer a tremendous punishment in the Hereafter"
  5,34,"except those who repent before you overpower them*, so know that God is Protectively Forgiving, Merciful"
  5,35,O you who believe ! fear God and seek the means of approach to Him and strive in His way so as to be successful
  5,36,"As for those who do not believe, even if all that is in the earth were theirs and the like of it with it(Double), to give as ransom for the punishment on the day of resurrection, it will certainly not be accepted from them and for them there will be a painful punishment"